oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Woodall family home, Sulphura
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Woodall family home, Sulphura. Shown are the four sons of James Lafayette Woodall and Mary Jane Bradley Woodall. They are James Oliver (1881-1946), William Carroll (1860-1926), Jesse M. (1877-1951) and Samuel M. (1861-?).
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
